::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod could see the love, in Arc's eyes. It reminded him about the
fact that he shouldn't try to go steady with Kamodia. He had really
asked her down, to talk, so he could learn more about her. He was
growing more attracted to her. Now he tryed his best to push the
thoughts of Kamodia out of his head. He wasn't going to push in on Arc's
turf.
